CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 15, 1960, pg. 2 reads: "At Mayors' Met, Discuss Urban Renewal - Shown at the Kennedy Conference of Urban Renewal, held Monday at the Hotel Penn-Sheraton and attended by mayors from 55 U.S. cities..."
TitMainTitle: Kennedy-Johnson presidential campaign: John F. Kennedy with Pennsylvania Governor David L. Lawrence, mingling with crowd behind table at the Penn Sheraton Hotel for presidential campaign
